docs.abstract: The president, who has been eager to cut a deal with Beijing, said the negotiators had forged a compromise on key issues but few details have been released.

docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Trump delayed his own deadline to increase tariffs on Chinese goods on Sunday as his administration continues a monthslong effort to persuade Beijing to make significant structural changes to its economy that have so far proved elusive.

docs.abstract: The guests discuss Richard Plepler’s influence on the network behind “Game of Thrones” — and ponder what lies ahead as AT&T asserts control.
docs.snippet: The guests discuss Richard Plepler’s influence on the network behind “Game of Thrones” — and ponder what lies ahead as AT&T asserts control.
docs.lead_paragraph: It was supposed to be another one of those glittery New York nights for Richard Plepler, with a screening of a new HBO documentary followed by a dinner party at Porter House, a spacious steak restaurant with a view of Central Park. But Mr. Plepler, the HBO chief executive, who announced his resignation on Thursday, was not among the roughly 200 filmmakers, screenwriters, journalists and HBO employees who filed in around 9:30.

headline.main: At an HBO Premiere Party, the C.E.O.’s Seat Was Empty
headline.print_headline: HBO’s Chief Was Absent On Big Night For Network
